<h1>Terms of Service</h1>
<p>
There's a few simple terms that we at bitZino would like to make sure you and us both agree upon. Please read them below, and if you don't agree to any of them, don't use our service. (But we'd love to hear what you don't agree with!). We do reserve the right to make changes to these terms by posting them here. If you have any questions or concerns about these terms, feel free to drop us a note by going to
