<b>Limitation of Liability:</b>
You acknowledge that the bitZino service allows you to gamble with the virtual currency known as bitcoin.
Therefore, during the normal course of using the service, you may lose some or all of the bitcoins you deposit. Under no circumstances will we be liable for any of your losses.
