<b>Inactive Accounts:</b>
We can't keep inactive accounts around forever. Therefore, we reserve the right to shut down inactive accounts and relinquish their funds. As long as you log in at least once every 6 months, your account will remain active. We may keep your account active longer as well. Before shutting down an inactive account, we will attempt to use whatever information you've provided us to contact you and try to return whatever funds are in it.
